<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910308-0006</DOCNO><DOCID>910308-0006.</DOCID><HL>   Who's News:   Optical Radiation Corp.</HL><DATE>03/08/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B5</SO><CO>   WNEWS ORCO</CO><IN>MEDICAL AND BIOTECHNOLOGY (MTC)</IN><LP>   OPTICAL RADIATION Corp. (Azusa, Calif.) -- Richard J.Pearson was named a director of this maker of opticalcomponents and systems, increasing the size of its board toseven members. Mr. Pearson, 65 years old, was president andchief operating officer of Avery Dennison Corp., a Pasadena,Calif., office products concern, until his retirement lastJune.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>